review: Went with the family and tried the Enchanted Forest. The room was set up with so much creativity and thought. Loved it.the staff was amazing, supportive, and managed to put up with our crazy family! They even offered a sneak peek into the other rooms - can't wait to go back!

room_title: Escape room "Enchanted Forest" by Zero Hour Escape Rooms in Duluth
review: We celebrated my son's 21st birthday as a family going through the Enchanted Forest. It was so much fun. Kudos to the staff putting up with our antics and little bumps in the road. I would encourage this as a great way to spend family fun time.
